imitingAuditRLAMessagingThumbnail.jpg\" \/><\/div>\n  <div class=\"right-col\">\n    <span class=\"publication-type\">resource<\/span>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/risk-limiting-audit-rla-messaging-guide-for-election-officials\/\" class=\"title\">Risk-Limiting Audit (RLA) Messaging Guide for Election Officials<\/a>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Date:<\/strong> September 2024<\/span>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Authors:<\/strong> Verified Voting<\/span>\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While each jurisdiction is unique and there is no one-size-fits-all model for risk-limiting audits, Verified Voting developed these messaging recommendations informed by findings from a research study conducted by Lake Research Partners.<\/span><\/p>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/risk-limiting-audit-rla-messaging-guide-for-election-officials\/\" class=\"blue-btn\">MORE<\/a>\n    <span class=\"publication-issue\"><\/span>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"publication-result\">\n  <div class=\"left-col\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/Thumbnail_Handout_CastingVotesSafely_2024-copy.jpg\" \/><\/div>\n  <div class=\"right-col\">\n    <span class=\"publication-type\">resource<\/span>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/consensus-studies-examining-internet-voting\/\" class=\"title\">Consensus Studies Examining Internet Voting<\/a>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Date:<\/strong> June 2024<\/span>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Authors:<\/strong> Verified Voting<\/span>\n    <p><\/p>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/consensus-studies-examining-internet-voting\/\" class=\"blue-btn\">MORE<\/a>\n    <span class=\"publication-issue\"><\/span>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"publication-result\">\n  <div class=\"left-col\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/20