nce that their<br \/>\nvotes were counted as cast. We address internet voting\u2019s dangers and discuss better options that enable voter<br \/>\nenfranchisement while still protecting the security of our elections.<\/p>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/casting-votes-safely-oct-2023\/\" class=\"blue-btn\">MORE<\/a>\n    <span class=\"publication-issue\">Internet Voting<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"publication-result\">\n  <div class=\"left-col\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-About-RLA-Pilots-2023.jpg\" \/><\/div>\n  <div class=\"right-col\">\n    <span class=\"publication-type\">resource<\/span>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/about-rla-pilots\/\" class=\"title\">About Risk-Limiting Audit Pilots<\/a>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Date:<\/strong> June 2023<\/span>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Authors:<\/strong> Verified Voting<\/span>\n    <p>Verified Voting&#8217;s downloadable resource on what risk-limiting audit pilots are and how Verified Voting helps jurisdictions across the country conduct them.<\/p>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/about-rla-pilots\/\" class=\"blue-btn\">MORE<\/a>\n    <span class=\"publication-issue\">Post-Election Audit<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"publication-result\">\n  <div class=\"left-col\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/VV-AnnualReport-2022-Cover.jpg\" \/><\/div>\n  <div class=\"right-col\">\n    <span class=\"publication-type\">Report<\/span>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/annual-report-2022\/\" class=\"title\">Annual Report 2022<\/a>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Date:<\/strong> May 31, 2023<\/span>\n    <span class=\"meta\"><strong>Authors:<\/strong> Verified Voting<\/span>\n    <p><\/p>\n  <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/publication\/annual-report-2022\/